article.description: — B.J. Mack had 17 points and Ryan Larson posted 19 points as Wofford topped Georgia Southern 70-52 on Sunday.
article.headline: Wofford beats Georgia Southern 70-52
article.story: SPARTANBURG, S.C. -- — B.J. Mack had 17 points and Ryan Larson posted 19 points as Wofford topped Georgia Southern 70-52 on Sunday. Max Klesmit had 13 points for Wofford (4-1), which earned its fourth consecutive home victory. Isaiah Bigelow added six rebounds. Andrei Savrasov had 10 points for the Eagles (4-1), whose four-game season-opening win streak came to an end. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
